main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 2759/1999 is amended as follows:
1. In Article 3, paragraph 1 is replaced by the following:
2. In Article 8, paragraph 4 is replaced by the following:
(a) ‘young farmers’ shall mean a farmer under 40 years of age at the time when the decision to grant support is taken, possessing adequate occupational skills and competence;
(b) ‘mountain areas’ shall mean mountain areas as defined in Article 18(1) of Regulation (EC) No 1257/1999;
(c) ‘public aid’ shall mean all such aid whether or not granted under the programme.’
